{{Underlinked|date=April 2014}}

'''Dillon's Reprise Room''', is a [[cabaret]], located on West 54th Street in [[Theater_District,_Manhattan|Manhattan's Theater District]].  Over the years, Dillons has been home to successful musical runs of "Our Sinatra," "Water Coolers," and most recently "[[Boobs! The Musical]],"<ref>{{cite web|last=Jones|first=Kenneth|title=Boobs! The Musical Busts Its Way Into NYC Theatre District|url=http://www.playbill.com/news/article/83375.html|work=Playbill|accessdate=29 July 2012|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080920035044/http://www.playbill.com/news/article/83375.html|archivedate=20 September 2008|df=}}</ref> as well as some of cabaret's top performers.

