===''Talking Tom and Friends''=== {{Main|Talking Tom and Friends (TV series)}} [[Outfit7|Outfit7 Limited]] launched an animated series called ''Talking Tom and Friends'' in 2015, based on the antics of Talking Tom and his Friends. The show is produced by the Austrian animation-studio 'arx anima'.
