{{Infobox building |name = Window on China Theme Park |native_name = 小人國主題樂園 |image = TW Win-On-China fdr.jpg |opening = |location = [[Longtan District, Taoyuan|Longtan]], [[Taoyuan City|Taoyuan]], [[Taiwan]] |building_type = [[Amusement park]] |start_date = |completion_date = 7 July 1984 |cost = |roof = |top_floor = |architectural = |observatory = |floor_count = |floor_area = |elevator_count = |architect = |structural_engineer = |main_contractor = |management = |owner = [[Chu Chung-hung]]<ref>{{cite web| url=http://www.woc.com.tw/web_en/html/01about/01.aspx | title=Introduction | publisher=Window on China Theme Park | location=Taiwan | accessdate=28 February 2014 }}</ref> |website = [http://www.woc.com.tw/index_en.aspx www.woc.com.tw] {{en icon}} |references = }}
The '''Window on China Theme Park''' ({{zh|c=小人國主題樂園|p=Xiǎorénguó Zhǔtí Lèyuán}}) is an [[amusement park]] in [[Longtan District, Taoyuan|Longtan District]], [[Taoyuan City]], [[Taiwan]].
